name: Reincarnate
description:
The past you have created with your current self, whether it be bad or good. Will you  give it up for another chance to start again and correct your mistakes? 

This is something that I've always thought and wanted to create a piece that presents these thoughts. I look at life and realise, there were a lot of mistakes I've made and if I could have another chance I would want to fix these mistakes.
